Step 1 - Check original LaTeX notes
\documentclass[11pt]{report}
\usepackage{amssymb,amsmath,amsfonts}
\usepackage{graphicx,epsf,caption}
\usepackage{titling,epstopdf,empheq}
\usepackage{xcolor}
\usepackage[pdftex,pdftitle={LA notes 2025.pdf},pdflang={en-GB}]{hyperref}
\hypersetup{
    colorlinks=true,
    linktoc=all,
    linkcolor=blue,
}
I spotted that the packages titling, epstopdf and empheq are not supported by Chirun.

Linear Algebra notes, courtesy of Professor John Hunton.

